dmca.title: Artist complains of mis-identified images
dmca.body:
Attn: Legal, DMCA complaints
Re: Notice of Copyright Infringement

** I had faxed a letter (in October) requesting images to be removed. Some have been removed though there are still a few remaining. I would like to kindly ask that ALL the images under 'emaleika' google search be removed.
There are 23 left. Thank you for all of your time and help in this.!!! 

RE: NOTICE OF COPYRIGHT INFRINGEMENT
As required under Sections 512(q)(3) and 512(d)(3) of the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (17 U.S.C.
